                <div class="md:flex border-b border-[#a9b4c6] border-dashed">
                    <div class="min-w-[160px] border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-[#a9b4c6] border-dashed p-4">
                        <span class="text-sm ">December 2020</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="w-[65px] h-[120px] bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat mb-2" style="background-image: url('https://www.megustaescribir.com/Images/COVER_MANUSCRIPT_106275');"></div>
                        <h1>Escritura creativa</h1>
                        <p class="text-sm ">I wrote a short story called 'Father`, a story of reflection on life and interpersonal relationships. You can read it in <a target="_blank" href="https://www.megustaescribir.com/obra/106275/padre" class="hover:text-teal-600 transition-all ease-in duration-150 underline">megustaescribir.com</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:flex">
                    <div class="min-w-[160px] border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-[#a9b4c6] border-dashed p-4">
                        <span class="text-sm ">2023 - Present</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="w-[100px] h-[80px] bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat rounded-md mb-2" style="background-image: url('https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2NzQ5ODYzLnBuZw==/315x250%23c/VueAIQ.png');"></div>
                        <h1>RPG Cozy Game with <a href="https://ellen0ra.itch.io" class="hover:text-teal-600 transition-all ease-in duration-150 underline">@Ellenora</a></h1>
                        <p class="text-sm ">As a video game enthusiast, one of my favorite hobbies is the development of games. This project is a cozy role -playing game like Stardew Valley and Animal Crossing. It develops completely in the Godot Game Engine and is intended as a collaboration project with Ellenora. This simple project serves as a practice for me and a step towards fulfilling one of my dreams: officially publishing a game. Through this project, its objective is to refine my skills in games development, work in collaborative creativity and contribute a pleasant game experience to others.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
